OL,3,CStormont to find #113m in next budget,
OL,4,Cgovernment confirms
OL,6,FThe UK Government has confirmed
OL,7,Fdetails of a #3.3billion funding
OL,8,Fpackage to support the restored power
OL,9,Fsharing administration in Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FThe settlement was outlined in a
OL,13,Fletter to Stormont Finance Minister
OL,14,FCaoimhe Archibald.
OL,16,FThe government described it as a
OL,17,F"significant, fair and generous"
OL,18,Fpackage. It has, however, said the
OL,19,FExecutive must raise #113m.
