OL,4,Cgovernment confirms
OL,6,FThe government said the plan included
OL,7,Fa requirement for the Executive to
OL,8,Fdeliver a balanced budget for 2024/25
OL,9,Fthat includes a minimum of #113
OL,10,Fmillion raised through locally
OL,11,Fgenerated income.
OL,13,FMinisters in Belfast will also be
OL,14,Fexpected to publish a "comprehensive
OL,15,Fand costed" long-term strategic
OL,16,Finfrastructure plan that sets out
OL,17,Fpriority areas for action and how they
OL,18,Fwill support prosperity and growth.
